text: Filippovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kadyrgulovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 49 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Filippovka
